---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Free PMO Tools | Lavelle Pty Ltd"
  description="Free PMO tools, checklists and project delivery resources from Lavelle Pty Ltd."
>
  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Lavelle Pty Ltd</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Free Tools</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Free PMO tools from Lavelle Pty Ltd are designed to help project managers and delivery leads improve control, governance and reporting without adding unnecessary process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FREE TOOLS LIST -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-xl mb-10">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Available Now</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Free Resources</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

        <!-- Project Recovery Checklist -->
        <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white hover:border-navy-300 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Free Project Recovery Checklist</h3>
            <span class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded">
              Free
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-5">
            A structured checklist for identifying whether a project has the basic controls needed to recover delivery confidence. Covers scope, governance, schedule, risks, issues, decisions, financials and stakeholder alignment.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/free-tools/project-recovery-checklist"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-navy-800 hover:bg-navy-900 rounded-md transition-colors"
            data-ga-event="free_tool_click"
            data-ga-label="Project Recovery Checklist"
          >
            View Checklist
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Business Case Readiness Checklist -->
        <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white opacity-80">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Business Case Readiness Checklist</h3>
            <span class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded">
              Coming Soon
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-5">
            A checklist for reviewing whether a business case proposal is ready for delegate approval. Covers problem definition, options analysis, financial model, benefits mapping and governance requirements.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-navy-700 border border-navy-300 hover:bg-navy-50 rounded-md transition-colors"
          >
            Notify Me
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Procurement Evaluation Checklist -->
        <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white opacity-80">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Procurement Evaluation Checklist</h3>
            <span class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded">
              Coming Soon
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-5">
            A checklist for designing a defensible evaluation process. Covers evaluation framework, scoring structure, probity obligations, clarification approach and BAFO management.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-navy-700 border border-navy-300 hover:bg-navy-50 rounded-md transition-colors"
          >
            Notify Me
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Steering Committee Checklist -->
        <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white opacity-80">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Steering Committee Reporting Checklist</h3>
            <span class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded">
              Coming Soon
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-5">
            A checklist for reviewing whether steering committee reports are structured to support governance. Covers report structure, RAG calibration, risk escalation and decision-making quality.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-navy-700 border border-navy-300 hover:bg-navy-50 rounded-md transition-colors"
          >
            Notify Me
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TEMPLATES CTA -->
  <section class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Need More Than a Checklist?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Lavelle Pty Ltd template packs include the full artefacts, working documents and structured guidance for each delivery challenge.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="/templates"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-navy-800 hover:bg-navy-900 rounded-md transition-colors"
          >
            View Templates
          </a>
          <a
            href="/consulting"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 border border-slate-300 hover:border-slate-400 rounded-md transition-colors"
          >
            View Consulting Services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
